snippet.title: on Sunday - PlayStation 4 Playthrough
snippet.description:
Minimalistic in style, this game brings you on an unusual Sunday walk.
Are these dangers of the outer world or of your own soul?

Developed and published by Acyntha
Also released for PlayStation 5
